text: Sardar Mohammad Jahangir is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Rajshahi-5. ==Career== Jahangir was elected to parliament from Rajshahi-5 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1973. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:1st Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Sardar Mohammad Jahangir
